For more details, refer to Troubleshooting.
.SH VERSION
.PP
v1.2 and above
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Perform a full backup of the replication group group1
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
>\ db.backup({Name:"backupName",Description:"backup\ group1",GroupName:"group1"})
\f[]
.fi
